text: Glan Pibwr Stream Section is a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Carmarthen & Dinefwr, Wales. Datasets for various species associated with this area, under a variety of designations, are available. ==See also== *List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Carmarthen & Dinefwr ==References== Category:Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Carmarthen & Dinefwr
